- if @default_soloist_script.present?
  #sw-default
    %h3 Option 1 - use our default install script w/ sensible defaults:
    %pre.code
      = @default_soloist_script.shell_install_command
    %p
      Executing this one command will install all of the software which is checked below.
    %p
      Note: If you'd rather download the script, you can save the
      = link_to "file", soloist_script_url(@default_soloist_script, :format => "sh")
      to your hard drive.



#sw-custom
  %h3 Option 2 - create a custom SoloWizard script:
  %p Select your recipes and click the button - we will build a custom script for you, which you can bookmark or share with others.
  = render "soloist_scripts/form"